        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong></strong><b>Tax Assistance for Crumbling Foundations Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals the tax rule in effect through 2025 that limits the deduction for personal casualty losses to losses attributable to a federally declared disaster. </p>]]>
